                    <span>I bought this book based onthe previous review; however, I found it to be too simple and superficial to get a real grasp of home networking processes and concepts. It'll tell you how to do it, but not great explanations about why. <BR>I recommend Moulton's SOHO Networking (2002) instead.</span>
                  
